11→| `${intent_id}` | `RecordId<"intent">` | `submit_intent` (existing) | `evaluate_rules`, `record_trace`, `view_flagged_intent`, `approve_or_veto` | SurrealDB `intent` table |
12→| `${applicable_policies}` | `PolicyRecord[]` | `load_policies` | `evaluate_rules` | Transient (query result) |
13→| `${policy_evaluation_trace}` | `PolicyTraceEntry[]` | `evaluate_rules` | `record_trace`, `view_flagged_intent`, `query_compliance` | `intent.evaluation.policy_trace` field |
14→| `${policy_gate_result}` | `PolicyGateResult` | `evaluate_rules` | `evaluateIntent()` pipeline | Transient (passed to existing evaluation pipeline) |
15→
16→## Type Definitions
17→
18→```typescript
19→// Policy evaluation trace — persisted on intent.evaluation
20→type PolicyTraceEntry = {
21→  policy_id: string;        // raw ID (not RecordId — stored in JSON)
22→  policy_version: string;
23→  rule_id: string;
24→  effect: "allow" | "deny";
25→  matched: boolean;         // did the condition match this intent?
26→  priority: number;
27→};
28→
29→// Full policy record from SurrealDB
30→type PolicyRecord = {
31→  id: RecordId<"policy">;
32→  title: string;
33→  description: string;
34→  version: string;
35→  status: "active" | "draft" | "deprecated" | "testing" | "superseded";
36→  selector: PolicySelector;
37→  rules: PolicyRule[];
38→  human_veto_required: boolean;
39→  max_ttl: string;          // SurrealDB duration as string
40→  created_by: RecordId<"identity">;
41→  created_at: Date;
42→  updated_at: Date;
43→};
44→
45→type PolicySelector = {
46→  workspace?: string;
47→  agent_role?: string;
48→  resource?: string;
49→};
50→
51→type PolicyRule = {
52→  id: string;
53→  condition: string;        // evaluatable condition string
54→  effect: "allow" | "deny";
55→  priority: number;
56→};
57→```
