59→## Data Flow
60→
61→```
62→create_policy → ${policy_id}, ${policy_version}
63→                    │
64→                    ▼
65→activate_policy → governing edges, protects edges
66→                    │
67→                    ▼
68→submit_intent → ${intent_id}
69→                    │
70→                    ▼
71→load_policies → ${applicable_policies[]}  (graph traversal)
72→                    │
73→                    ▼
74→evaluate_rules → ${policy_gate_result} + ${policy_evaluation_trace}
75→                    │
76→                    ├──→ record_trace (persists trace on intent)
77→                    │
78→                    ├──→ view_flagged_intent (reviewer sees trace)
79→                    │
80→                    └──→ query_compliance (auditor queries by policy version)
81→```
